query_en: When did the person who buried the bones of the 72 martyrs of Huanghuagang (黄花岗七十二烈士) become the head of the Guangzhou Branch of the Tongmenghui (同盟会广州分会) ?
answer_en: The remains of the 72 martyrs of Huanghuagang were buried by Pan Dawei (潘达微), who became the head of the Guangzhou branch of the Tongmenghui (同盟会广州分会) in 1909.

query_zh: 韩国第二位因弹劾而下台的总统在哪一年参与了独立团队调查选举期间的股价操纵事件？
answer_zh: 韩国第二位因弹劾而下台的总统是尹锡悦，他在2008年参与了独立团队调查选举期间的股价操纵事件
query_en: In which year did South Korea's second president to be removed from office by impeachment join an independent team investigating stock price manipulation during the election?
answer_en: South Korea's second president to be removed from office by impeachment is Yun Seok-yeol (윤석열), and he was part of an independent team investigating stock price manipulation during the 2008 election.

query_zh: ISTAT代码为084019的市镇2009年的人口密度是多少
answer_zh: ISTAT代码为084019的市镇是约波洛詹卡克肖（Joppolo Giancaxio）,它在2009年的人口密度是65.3人/平方公里
query_en: What was the population density in 2009 for municipalities with ISTAT code 084019
answer_en: The municipality with ISTAT code 084019 is Joppolo Giancaxio, which had a population density of 65.3 inhabitants per square kilometer in 2009.

query_zh: 于1968年退出华沙条约组织（Организация Варшавского Договора）的国家在退出那一年的人民议会主席团主席什么时候去世？
answer_zh: 1968年退出华沙条约组织（Организация Варшавского Договора）的是阿尔巴尼亚。阿尔巴尼亚人民议会主席团主席是哈吉·列希（Haxhi Lleshi）。哈吉·列希（Haxhi Lleshi）于1998年去世。
query_en: When did the Chairman of the Presidium of the People's Assembly of the country that withdrew from the Warsaw Pact in 1968 pass away?
answer_en: Albania withdrew from the Warsaw Pact in 1968. The chairman of the Presidium of the Albanian People's Assembly was Haxhi Lleshi. Haxhi Lleshi died in 1998.

query_zh: 嘉庆十三年八月初二被调任广西学政的沈学厚出生的省份在中国2020年第七次人口普查分省指标中排名第几位？
answer_zh: 沈学厚出生在浙江省，浙江省在中国2020年第七次人口普查分省指标中排名第8位

query_zh: 2015年电影《玩转脑朋友》（Inside Out）中韦莉妈妈的香港配音演员于2015年出演了一部电影，她在那部电影中出演了什么角色？
answer_zh: 韦莉妈妈的香港配音演员是谭玉瑛，谭玉瑛在2015年电影《哪一天我们会飞》中饰英仁书院副校长
query_en: In the 2015 film Inside Out, the Hong Kong voice actress of Riley's mom appeared in a movie in 2015. What role did she play in that movie?

query_zh: 截至2024年，在2016年香港电影《此情此刻》（The Moment）中饰史提芬的演员出演的舞台剧的名字是什么？
answer_zh: 饰史提芬的演员是谭玉瑛，她在2024年前出只演过的舞台剧《寒武纪与威士忌》

answer_en: The actor who plays Stephen (史提芬) is Helen Tam Yuk Ying (谭玉瑛), who has only performed in the stage play "Cambrian and Whiskey" (《寒武纪与威士忌》) before 2024.

query_zh: 香港时装喜剧《飞越十八层》（英语：You Only Live Twice）的主题曲的编曲者在2002年获得了什么奖？
answer_zh: 主题曲是《难为正邪定分界》，编曲者是顾嘉煇，顾嘉煇于2002年获得金曲银禧荣誉大奖
query_en: What award did the arranger of the theme song for the Hong Kong fashion comedy "You Only Live Twice" win in 2002?
answer_en: The theme song is "It's Hard to Determine the Line Between Good and Evil" (难为正邪定分界), arranged by Joseph Koo Kar Fai (顾嘉煇), who won the Silver Jubilee Honorary Award（金曲银禧荣誉大奖）

query_zh: 2001年，印度阿努普尔县（印地语：अनूपपुर, Anuppur）的首府的识字率是多少？

query_zh: 1998年上映的香港剧情电影《新羔羊医生》（Trust Me U Die）中角色陈森的粤语配音员的妻子为2005年电影《不死狗》（Unleashed）中的哪一位角色配了音？

answer_en: Luo Weijie, the Cantonese voice actor for the character Chen Sen in the 1998 Hong Kong film "New Lamb Doctor" (Trust Me U Die), has a wife named Liu Huiyun, who dubbed the role of Victoria in the 2005 film "Unleashed".

query_zh: 1998年上映的香港剧情电影《新羔羊医生》（Trust Me U Die）的监制为1996年上映的哪部电影配了音？
answer_zh: 其监制邓荣銾在1996年为电影《危险任务》（Dangerous Assignment）中的角色“阿聪”进行了粤语配音。
query_en: Who was the producer of the 1998 Hong Kong film "Trust Me U Die" (the one whose Chinese surname is Deng), and which movie did he dub a voice for in 1996?
answer_en: Its producer Charles Tang Wing Hung provided the Cantonese dubbing for the character "A Cong" in the movie "Dangerous Assignment" in 1996.

query_zh: 香港男配音员罗伟杰的妻子为2007年的韩剧《狗与狼的时间》（개와 늑대의 시간）中的哪一位角色配了音？
answer_zh: 罗伟杰的妻子刘惠云在《狗与狼的时间》中为徐智友配音
query_en: For which character in the 2007 Korean drama "Dog and Wolf's Time" (개와 늑대의 시간) did the wife of Hong Kong male voice actor Ronny Wu provide the voice?
answer_en: Liu Huiyun, the wife of Hong Kong male voice actor Luo Weijie, provided the voice for the character Xu Zhiyou in the 2007 Korean drama "Dog and Wolf's Time" (개와 늑대의 시간).

query_zh: 台湾歌手潘玮柏的第八张国语专辑中，时长超过5分钟的那首歌的作词者还参与了该专辑中哪首歌的作词？
answer_zh: 专辑《808》中时长超过5分钟的歌曲是《未来爱情》，其作曲NHL没有参与该专辑中其他歌曲的作词
query_en: In Taiwanese singer Wilber Pan's 8th Mandarin album, which song's lyrics were written by the same person who wrote the lyrics for the song that's over 5 minutes long?
answer_en: In the album "808", the song exceeding 5 minutes is "Future Love". Its composer, NHL, didn't write lyrics for any other song in the album, so it's a false premise.

query_zh: 曾担任香港驻三藩市经济贸易办事处处长的曾舜雯（英语：Jacko Tsang Shun-man）在就读美国维思大学之前所读的学校（不是小学）的创校校长于哪一年离任？
answer_zh: 曾舜雯在就读美国维思大学之前所读的学校是香港李宝椿联合世界书院，其创校校长大卫·威尔金森博士于1994年离任
query_en: Before attending Wesleyan University in the United States, Jacko Tsang Shun-man (曾舜雯), former Director of the Hong Kong Economic and Trade Office in San Francisco, studied at a school (not primary school). Who founded that school and in which year did he/she leave office?
answer_en: The school that Jacko Tsang Shun-man (曾舜雯) attended before studying at Wesleyan University in the US is the Li Po Chun United World College of Hong Kong (香港李宝椿联合世界书院), whose founding principal, Dr. David Wilkinson, left office in 1994.

query_zh: 于1987年7月19日出生的前香港新闻从业员、现执业大律师刘晋安（英语：Andrew Christopher Lau Chun On）就读预科的学校的第二任校长于哪一年离职？
answer_zh: 该学校是香港李宝椿联合世界书院，其第二任校长布莱尔·佛斯特（Mr. Blair Forster）于2003年因病去世而结束任期
query_en: Andrew Christopher Lau Chun On (刘晋安), a former Hong Kong journalist and current practicing barrister born on July 19, 1987, attended a secondary school whose second principal left office in which year?
answer_en: The school is Li Po Chun United World College of Hong Kong. Its second principal, Mr. Blair Forster, passed away due to illness in 2003, which marked the end of his term in office.

query_zh: 香港建制派政治人物，新民党中央委员李梓敬（英语：Dominic Lee Tsz-king）就读预科的学校在2005年的校长是谁？
answer_zh: 该学校是香港李宝椿联合世界书院，其在2005年的校长是郭林同博士（Dr. Stephen Codrington）

answer_en: The school is Li Po Chun United World College of Hong Kong (香港李宝椿联合世界书院). In 2005, its principal was Dr. Stephen Codrington.

query_zh: 香港建制派政治人物，新民党中央委员李梓敬（英语：Dominic Lee Tsz-king）就读的小学于哪一年开始招收女生？
answer_zh: 该学校是拔萃小学（Diocesan Preparatory School），2005年开始招收女生
query_en: Which year did the elementary school attended by Dominic Lee Tsz-king, a Hong Kong pro-establishment political figure and member of the New People's Party Central Committee, begin admitting girls?
answer_en: The school is Diocesan Preparatory School, which began admitting girls in 2005.

query_zh: 美国历史上第一个民歌手的组织成立时的主席的长兄是什么职业？
answer_zh: 美国历史上第一个民歌手的组织“人民之歌”（People's Songs）成立时的主席是皮特·西格（Pete Seeger），他的长兄查尔斯·西格（Charles Seeger III）是一位射电天文学家。
query_en: What was the profession of the eldest brother of the chairman when the first folk singers' organization the in United States was established?
answer_en: When the first folk singers' organization in U.S. history, People's Songs, was established, its chairman was Pete Seeger, whose eldest brother, Charles Seeger III, was a radio astronomer.

query_zh: 在芝加哥大学法学院（University of Chicago Law School）任Harry Kalven Jr. 法学教授职位的William Patrick Baude的父亲在2000年任职的学院是哪一年建立的？

answer_en: William Patrick Baude's father, Patrick L. Baude, worked at Indiana University Maurer School of Law in 2000, which was established in 1842.

query_zh: 在1932年出生的曾任中国科学院大连化学物理研究所研究员的周良模出生的省份在2019年常住人口在10,000人以上的少数民族共有多少个？

query_zh: 2004年印度国会大选获胜党党主席出生地（精确到镇）在2009年时人口密度是多少

answer_en: The Congress won the Indian parliamentary election on May 13, 2004. The Congress will support the party’s chairman Sonya Gandhi as prime minister. His birthplace, Lushana, has a population density of 83.4 people/square kilometer (2009)

query_zh: 《追随》（1998年）的导演参与创作的第二部纪录片在哪个电影节首映？
answer_zh: 《追随》（1998年）的导演是克里斯托弗·诺兰。他创作的第二部纪录片《阴阳相成》（Side by Side）首映于第62届柏林电影节。
query_en: At which film festival did the second documentary co-created by the director of Following (1998) premiere?
answer_en: Christopher Nolan directed Following (1998). His second documentary Side by Side premiered at the 62nd Berlin Film Festival.

query_zh: 《追随》（1998年）的导演创作的2023年上映的电影的男性主演中，最早担任其他作品的编剧的是？
answer_zh: 《追随》（1998年）的导演是克里斯托弗·诺兰。克里斯托弗·诺兰创作的《奥本海默》在2023年上映。《奥本海默》的男性主演中，小罗伯特唐尼是担任编剧最早的人，他在1993年担任The Last Party的编剧。
query_en: Among the main male actors in the film released in 2023, which was directed by the director of "Follow" (1998), who was the first to serve as the screenwriter of other works?
answer_en: Following (1998) was directed by Christopher Nolan. Oppenheimer, created by Christopher Nolan, was released in 2023. Among the male leading actors of Oppenheimer, Robert Downey Jr. was the first person to serve as a screenwriter. He served as the screenwriter of The Last Party in 1993.

query_zh: 在2018年的皇室战争职业联赛中，五大赛区中第二个展开春季赛的赛区是哪个？它的春季赛开始时间和首届皇室战全球总决赛相隔多少天？
answer_zh: 第二个展开春季赛的赛区是亚洲赛区，在2018年4月27日。全球总决赛在2018年12月1日。两者相隔218天
query_en: In the first Clash Royale League, which of the five major regions started the spring season second? How many days are there between the start of the spring season in that region and the first Clash Royale World Finals?
answer_en: The second region to start the Spring Season is the Asia region, on April 27, 2018. The World Finals were on December 1, 2018. The two are 218 days apart.

query_zh: 根据联合国在2017年发表的修订版“世界人口展望”预测制作的世界主权国家和地区人口列表中，人口数排名第81位的国家的现任（2025年）总统毕业的大学是在什么时间创立的？
answer_zh: 人口数排名第81位的国家是贝宁，其总统帕特里斯·塔隆（Patrice Talon）毕业的大学是切克·安塔·迪奥普大学（Cheikh Anta Diop University）的创立时间是1957/02/24
query_en: Which country ranks 81st in terms of population in the world's sovereign countries and regions according to the revised version of the "World Population Prospects" published by the United Nations in 2017? When was the university that the current (2025) president of this country graduated from founded?
answer_en: The country ranked 81st in terms of population is Benin, whose president in 2025, Patrice Talon, graduated from Cheikh Anta Diop University, which was founded on 1957/02/24

query_zh: 智利共和国的第十一任总统和妻子共生育几个孩子？
answer_zh: 智利共和国的第十一任总统何塞·曼努埃尔·巴尔马塞达（José Manuel Balmaceda）有8个孩子
query_en: How many children did the 11th President of the Republic of Chile have with his wife?
answer_en: The 11th President of the Republic of Chile José Manuel Balmaceda has 8 children

query_zh: 迷笛音乐节的第十届中国摇滚迷笛奖年度最佳的获奖艺人2024在日本巡演的主题名为？
answer_zh: 迷笛音乐节的第十届中国摇滚迷笛奖年度最佳的获奖艺人为李志。他2024年在日本的巡演名为“叁缺壹”
query_en: What was the theme of the 2024 tour in Japan by the artist who won the "Best Artist of the Year" award at the 10th Midi Music Festival's China Rock Midi Awards?
answer_en: Li Zhi won the "Best Artist of the Year" award at the 10th Midi Music Festival's China Rock Midi Awards. His tour in Japan in 2024 was titled "Three Missing One"（“叁缺壹”）

query_zh: 2020马来西亚钜富榜排名第11位的富豪在哪里读的中学

query_en: Where did the 11th richest person on the 2020 list of Malaysian billionaires attend secondary school?
answer_en: This tycoon is Francis Yeoh Sock Ping, and his secondary school is Victoria Institution in Kuala Lumpur.

query_zh: 2017马来西亚钜富榜排名第25位的富豪出生于哪一天

query_zh: Baby Reindeer（2024）的执行制作人（Executive producer）中有一位曾在2007年执导过另一部作品，它的分类和时长是？
answer_zh: 该执行制作人是Richard Gadd，他在2007年执导的Fully-Charged Videos是动作喜剧，时长2h30m
query_en: One of the executive producers of Baby Reindeer directed another work in 2007. What is this work's genre and duration?

query_zh: 有一位出生于1867年的西班牙作家，她属于西班牙第一个女电报员组织，死于1959年，她的笔名是？
answer_zh: 这位西班牙作家是康苏埃洛·阿尔瓦雷斯·普尔（Consuelo Álvarez Pool），她的的笔名是Violeta
query_en: A Spanish writer born in 1867, who belonged to Spain's first female telegraphers' organization and died in 1959, what was her pen name?
answer_en: This Spanish writer is Consuelo Álvarez Pool, also known by her pen name Violeta

query_zh: 20-21世纪有一位寿命101岁的中美洲散文和十四行诗诗歌作家，她在哪里取得学士学位？
answer_zh: 该作家是安吉丽娜·阿库尼亚（Angelina Acuña），她在Instituto Normal Central para Señoritas Belén获得学士学位
query_en: A Central American essayist and sonnet poet who lived to be 101 years old in the 20th-21st centuries, where did she obtain her bachelor's degree?
answer_en: This writer is Angelina Acuña, who received her bachelor's degree from the Instituto Normal Central para Señoritas Belén

query_zh: Ofrenda Lirica a Guatemala (1939)的作者曾经担任过访问教授的学校的校训是什么？
answer_zh: Ofrenda Lirica a Guatemala (1939)的作者是安吉丽娜·阿库尼亚（Angelina Acuña），她担任过佛罗里达南方学院的访问教授。佛罗里达南方学院的校训是光明，智慧，法律（Light, Wisdom, Law）
query_en: What is the motto of the school where the author of Ofrenda Lirica a Guatemala (1939) once served as a visiting professor?
answer_en: Ofrenda Lirica a Guatemala (1939) was written by Angelina Acuña, who was a visiting professor at Florida Southern College. The college's motto is Light, Wisdom, Law.

query_zh: 2024年2月29日有一个国家的前任总统逝世，这个国家的2025年4月的总统的上一任在哪里取得了他的博士学位？
answer_zh: 2024年2月29日坦桑尼亚前总统阿里·哈桑·姆维尼（Ali Hassan Mwinyi）逝世。2025年四月坦桑尼亚总统的前一任是约翰·马古富利（John Pombe Joseph Magufuli）。约翰·马古富利（John Pombe Joseph Magufuli）在达累斯萨拉姆大学（University of Dar es Salaam）取得博士学位
query_en: On February 29, 2024, the former president of a country passed away. Where did the president in April 2025 of this country obtain his doctoral degree?
answer_en: Ali Hassan Mwinyi, the former president of Tanzania, died on February 29, 2024. The previous president of Tanzania in April 2025 was John Pombe Joseph Magufuli. John Pombe Joseph Magufuli obtained his doctorate from the University of Dar es Salaam.

query_zh: 1923年的冰岛总理（prime minister）在1932年创作了什么戏剧
answer_zh: 1923年的冰岛总理西格杜尔·艾格兹（Sigurður Eggerz）在1932年创作了戏剧《在黑暗中》（Í sortanum）
query_en: What play was written by the Icelandic prime minister of 1923 in 1932?
answer_en: Sigurður Eggerz, Iceland's Prime Minister in 1923, wrote the play Í sortanum (In the Dark) in 1932.

query_zh: 由 Sean Farley编剧的电影Neighborhood Watch的导演在2008年出演的电影的导演是谁
answer_zh: 由 Sean Farley编剧的电影Neighborhood Watch的导演是Duncan Skiles。他在2008年出演了I Can See You，其导演是Graham Reznick
query_en: Who was the director of the movie in which the director of the 2008 film directed by Sean Farley, Neighborhood Watch, appeared?
answer_en: Duncan Skiles directed Neighborhood Watch, written by Sean Farley. He also starred in I Can See You in 2008, directed by Graham Reznick.

query_zh: 出生于1884年的一位精神分析学家曾经师从欧根·布洛伊勒，他在哪所学校学习参加法语课程？
answer_zh: 这位精神分析师是赫尔曼·罗夏（Hermann Rorschach），他在第戎大学（University of Dijon）参加法语课程
query_en: At which school did a psychoanalyst born in 1884, who studied under Eugen Bleuler, take French classes?
answer_en: The psychoanalyst was Hermann Rorschach, who took French classes at the University of Dijon.

query_zh: 第51届金马奖的评审团主席凭借哪部作品获得第12届澳门国际电影节的最佳女主角提名？
answer_zh: 第51届金马奖的评审团主席为陈冲，她凭借《误杀》获得第12届澳门国际电影节的最佳女主角提名
query_en: Which film earned the chairperson of the jury of the 51st Golden Horse Awards a Best Actress nomination at the 12th Macau International Film Festival?
answer_en: Chen Chong (陈冲), the jury chairperson for the 51st Golden Horse Awards, was nominated for Best Actress at the 12th Macau International Film Festival for her role in "Sheep Without a Shepherd"(《误杀》).

query_zh: 第39届金马奖的评审团主席在2006年之后第二次入围戛纳电影节的作品是？
answer_zh: 第39届金马奖的评审团主席是侯孝贤，他2016年后第二次入围戛纳电影节的作品是《刺客聂隐娘》
query_en: Which film earned the chairperson of the jury at the 39th Golden Horse Awards their second nomination at the Cannes Film Festival after 2006?
answer_en: The jury chairman of the 39th Golden Horse Awards is Hou Hsiao-hsien (侯孝贤), whose second entry into the Cannes Film Festival after 2006 is The Assassin (《刺客聂隐娘》)

query_zh: 第九届夏季奥林匹克运动会宣布开幕者的私生子在1986年被判处四年半的刑期，他犯下了什么罪？
answer_zh: 第九届夏季奥林匹克运动会宣布开幕者是Duke Henry of Mecklenburg-Schwerin，他的私生子Pim Lier在1986年犯下谋杀罪被判处四年半刑期。
query_en: The illegitimate son of the announcer of the opening of the 9th Summer Olympic Games was sentenced to four and a half years in prison in 1986. What crime did he commit?
answer_en: The Ninth Summer Olympic Games were opened by Duke Henry of Mecklenburg-Schwerin, whose illegitimate son Pim Lier was sentenced to four and a half years in prison for murder in 1986.

query_zh: 第52届金马奖的评审团主席自2010年以来第二次获得香港电影金像奖提名是凭借哪部作品？
answer_zh: 第52届金马奖的评审团主席是陈国富，他2010年后第二次获得香港电影金像奖提名是凭借作品《人间·小团圆》
query_en: For which work did the chairman of the jury of the 52nd Golden Horse Awards receive a nomination for the Hong Kong Film Awards for the second time since 2010?
answer_en: The chairman of the jury for the 52nd Golden Horse Awards is Chen Guofu (陈国富), who was nominated for the Hong Kong Film Awards for the second time since 2010 for his work "Aberdeen" (《人间·小团圆》)

query_zh: 截至2025年，谁曾经连续两年担任台湾金曲奖的评审团主席？
query_en: Who served as the chairman of the Golden Melody Awards jury for two consecutive years before 2025?
answer_en: Liu Yawen (刘亚文), in 2006 and 2007. Ni Chonghua (倪重华), in 2013 and 2014.

query_zh: 根据联合国在2017年发表的修订版“世界人口展望”预测制作的世界主权国家和地区人口列表中人口数排名第153名的国家是哪个？该国家在2025年5月的在任总统有几个亲生哥哥姐姐?
answer_zh: 人口数排名第153名的国家是特立尼达和多巴哥，其总统是克里斯汀·坎加洛（Christine Kangaloo）。Christine Kangaloo有四个哥哥姐姐（她是七个孩子中的第五个）
query_en: Which country ranks 153rd in terms of population in the world's sovereign countries and regions according to the revised version of the "World Population Prospects" published by the United Nations in 2017? How many older siblings does the president of this country have in May 2025?
answer_en: The country ranked 153rd is Trinidad and Tobago, whose president is Christine Kangaloo. Christine Kangaloo has four older siblings (she is the fifth of seven children).

query_zh: 截至2025年，台湾金曲奖历史上有几次四个人共同主持颁奖典礼？
query_en: As of 2025, how many times has the Taiwan Golden Melody Awards ceremony been co-hosted by four people?
answer_en: 2 times, in 2001 and 2008

query_zh: 某个国家的第50任总统同时是一位喜剧演员，他在哪里获得硕士学位？
answer_zh: 这位总统是危地马拉第50任总统吉米·莫拉莱斯（Jimmy Morales ），他从马里亚诺·加尔韦斯大学（Mariano Gálvez University）获得高级战略研究硕士学位，从危地马拉泛美大学（Universidad Panamericana de Guatemala）获得媒体管理硕士学位
query_en: The 50th president of a certain country is also a comedian. Where did he get his master's degree?
answer_en: The president is Jimmy Morales, the 50th president of Guatemala. He holds a master's degree in strategic studies with a specialization in security and defense from Mariano Gálvez University and a master's degree in media management from Universidad Panamericana de Guatemala.

query_zh: 2012年欧盟中基尼系数最低的国家在2025年4月的总统从哪里取得博士学位？
answer_zh: 2012年欧盟中基尼系数（Gini coefficient）最低的国家是斯洛文尼亚。斯洛文尼亚在2025年4月的总统是娜塔莎·皮尔茨·穆萨尔（Nataša Pirc Musar），她从维也纳大学法学院（University of Vienna's Faculty of Law ）获得博士学位。
query_en: Where did the president in April 2025 of the country with the lowest Gini coefficient in the European Union in 2012 obtain his doctoral degree?
answer_en: The country with the lowest Gini coefficient in the EU in 2012 was Slovenia. Slovenia's president in April 2025 is Nataša Pirc Musar, who holds a doctorate from the University of Vienna's Faculty of Law.
